data.description: This delightful property features a spacious 2,300-square-foot home, thoughtfully designed with the primary bedroom conveniently situated on the main floor. Offering a total of four bedrooms and two baths, it provides abundant space for your family's comfort. The lower level of the home boasts a generously sized family room, complete with ample shelving, an open kitchen that seamlessly connects to the dining area, and a sunken living room adorned with a ceiling fan and a cozy pellet stove. The adjoining sunroom opens up to a covered porch on one side and an inviting open patio on the other, Additional amenities on the property include a two-car garage, a substantial barn featuring a hay loft, and a secondary storage building. An RV cover stands ready to shelter your recreational vehicles, while the entertaining treehouse has been recently refurbished and enclosed, creating a tranquil retreat. The landscape is graced with flourishing fruit trees, bountiful blueberries, and luscious grapes. There's even a second stone patio thoughtfully designed for gatherings. The property's tall timbers, spread across its generous 2.49-acre expanse, contribute to a serene and park-like atmosphere that beckons you to relax and enjoy. For added security and convenience, the property is fully enclosed with fencing and features an electric gate.
